title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Rotterdam  - version 1.2
description:
In this video we will look at the latest version the scenery package for the city of Rotterdam. The scenery package is based on Google maps and adds a lot of detail including POI's which are  making it even nicer to fly over this city.

If you want to give the scenery a try visit the link below to download it
https://flightsim.to/file/49139/rotterdam
